# Project Structure

This document describes the folder structure of the Retail Order Automation System.

## Root Directory

retail-order-system-bachelor/

- README.md – project overview and setup instructions
- backend – main application code

## Backend Structure

backend/

### main.py
Main FastAPI application file.  
Contains API endpoints and connects the application components.

### database/

Handles database configuration and data models.

- database.py – database connection and session setup
- models.py – SQLAlchemy database models
- crud.py – database operations

### services/

Contains business logic of the system.

- calculator.py – order calculation algorithm
- validator.py – Excel data validation logic

### templates/

HTML templates rendered by FastAPI using Jinja2.

- base.html – main layout
- upload.html – Excel upload interface
- history.html – order history page
- dashboard.html – analytics dashboard

### static/

Static assets used by the frontend.

- css/style.css – application styles